        <mxCell value="&lt;b&gt;Human researcher&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Defines goal&lt;br&gt;Handles VPN/MFA/auth&lt;br&gt;Approves risky choices" style="rounded=1;arcSize=12;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#3178C6;fontFamily=Inter;fontSize=14;fontColor=#102033;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=16;spacingTop=12;shadow=1;" vertex="1" parent="1" id="human">
